From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: conda-forge staged-recipes <conda-forge@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 28 May 2026 19:10:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Remove root build helper from packaged source

The root-level build.py is an upstream CI helper, not part of the Python
package build. Its name shadows the PyPA build package while conda initializes
plugins before running the recipe script.
---
 build.py | 11 -----------
 1 file changed, 11 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100755 build.py

diff --git a/build.py b/build.py
deleted file mode 100755
index 61e3f7d..0000000
--- a/build.py
+++ /dev/null
@@ -1,11 +0,0 @@
-#!/usr/bin/env python
-
-import sys
-from pathlib import Path
-
-path = Path(__file__).resolve().parent / ".github" / "workflows" / "scripts"
-sys.path.insert(0, str(path))
-
-import ti_build.entry
-
-sys.exit(ti_build.entry.main())
-- 
2.51.0

